rComments: She's definitely one of my favourite profs. She's incredibly nice and caring. She never makes you feel like you're dumb. She loves it when you participate. She makes her classes so interesting. If I could pick her to teach me for all of my courses, I would in a heartbeat. I wish I took her classes in person, I can imagine how great it would've been

She is a sweetheart. Her lectures are inspiring and engaging, clear grading criteria on the weekly assignments. Midterm was clear, take home exam was easy as well. She cares for her students and she makes great effort to know everyone's name. I have the pleasure of taking another class with her for the winter semester.
